{"title":"K-Edge teases first aftermarket computer mount for new Wahoo BOLT w/ 2.0 Aero Mount","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/05/26/k-edge-teases-first-aftermarket-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-bolt-w-2-0-aero-mount/","date":1622050204000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>Leave it to the accessory mounting wizards at K-Edge to be on the ball when it comes to new computer mounts. Just a few hours after we <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/05/25/wahoo-elemnt-bolt-gps-strikes-back-w-color-screen-increased-storage-usb-c-charging-more/\">posted the news of Wahoo’s newest GPS computer with a color screen</a>, K-Edge let us know that a new mount was already in the works.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130908/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130908/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-4.jpg\" alt=\"K-EDGE new Wahoo BOLT 2.0 Aero Mount rendering\" width=\"549\" height=\"261\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130908/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-4.jpg 549w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130908/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-4-297x141.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130908/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-4-120x57.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 549px) 100vw, 549px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130908/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-4.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130908/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-4.jpg 549w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130908/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-4-297x141.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130908/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-4-120x57.jpg 120w\"></a></p><p>Since the new ELEMNT BOLT is slightly larger than the previous model, a new mount is needed to take full advantage of any aero gains (it also just looks better if it fits properly without gaps). As mentioned previously, the new computers will still fit on older mounts, they’ll just leave a gap.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130900/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130900/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-1.jpg\" alt=\"K-EDGE new Wahoo BOLT 2.0 Aero Mount rendering\" width=\"313\" height=\"219\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130900/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-1.jpg 313w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130900/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-1-297x208.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130900/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-1-120x84.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130900/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-1-100x70.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 313px) 100vw, 313px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130900/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-1.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130900/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-1.jpg 313w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130900/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-1-297x208.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130900/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-1-120x84.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130900/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-1-100x70.jpg 100w\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130905/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26130905/K-Edge-aluminum-aero-handlebar-computer-mount-for-new-wahoo-ELEMNT-BOLT-color-3.jpg\" alt=\"K-EDGE new Wahoo BOLT 2.0 Aero Mount rendering\" width=\"585\" height=\"185\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-